      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ここが撮影で使うプールか。ライブでミクと歌った曲が\n好評で、MVまで一緒に撮影することになるなんてな",
      "startTime": 5.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-03.m4a",
          "delay": 3866.6666666999995,
          "startTime": 9.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-03.m4a",
          "delay": 4700,
          "startTime": 9.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "って、すず、芽衣……早速プールに飛び込むんじゃない\n涼みに来た訳じゃないんだぞ",
      "startTime": 14.7666666031,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2696.7118262999998,
          "startTime": 17.4633784294
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、使えそうな小道具は水鉄砲と浮き輪……\nならあのポーズが……こう、かしら？",
      "startTime": 23.5333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、あのグラビア雑誌で見たポーズが活かせそうね\nこんな感じでもっと儚さを……うーん……",
      "startTime": 33.2333325068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　沙季だけ一人でずっと歩き回ったり\n唸ったりしているが……まさか調子が悪いのか？",
      "startTime": 42.5999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "はっ……すみません、ご心配をお掛けしました\nですが、調子は悪いどころか、良過ぎるぐらいです",
      "startTime": 51.5333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "本当か？　九月に入ったとはいえまだ日差しも強い\n熱中症だったら大変だぞ、無理はしないでくれよ",
      "startTime": 60.599999237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。少し、集中し過ぎていただけですから\nこの後の撮影のために、イメトレをしていたんです",
      "startTime": 69.599999237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "歩き回っていたのは、撮影の際に使えそうな小道具や\nポーズが映えそうな場所を探していて",
      "startTime": 77.6333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。悪い、俺も心配し過ぎたな\n努力家な沙季らしい理由で安心したよ",
      "startTime": 85.0666659037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "しかし、本番前から練習を怠らないのはさすがだな\n真っ先に遊びだしたすず達も、少しは見習ってほしいよ",
      "startTime": 92.5333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "とんでもない！　私が慎重過ぎるだけですから\nそれに本番前はリラックスも大事だと思いますよ",
      "startTime": 101.3333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "リラックスか。確かにまだ時間にも余裕があるし\n何よりミクも楽しそうにしているしな",
      "startTime": 110.2333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことだったら\n沙季も一緒に交ざって遊んできてもいいんだぞ？",
      "startTime": 114.599999237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、私は……このままイメトレを続けます\n浮かれて本番で空回りする訳にはいきませんから",
      "startTime": 122.1333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "少し慎重過ぎる気もするけどな\n今の沙季だったら、そんな心配はいらないと思うよ",
      "startTime": 129.5333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nですが、今日はいつも以上に慎重にいきたいんです",
      "startTime": 135.4333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "あのバーチャルシンガー、ミクさんのライブに\nゲスト出演出来た上、一緒に新曲まで作れて……",
      "startTime": 142.0333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "さらにはMVでも共演出来るなんて、本当に夢みたいで\n私、今もドキドキしているんです……！",
      "startTime": 152.4333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、油断だけはする訳にはいかないんです\nこのチャンスを無駄にしないためにも！",
      "startTime": 160.0333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（無駄にしないためにも、か……）\n（そういえばこの話を持ってきた時……）",
      "startTime": 167.2666659037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？\n『君の残り香』のMVで、ミクさんと共演っ！？",
      "startTime": 173.7666659037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、少し早い再会で俺も驚いたよ\n沙季は確か、ミクの大ファンだったよな？",
      "startTime": 181.4333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　トリエルやリズノワとの楽曲はもちろん\nミクさんの曲は沢山聴いています！",
      "startTime": 188.399999237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい、今日はこのプレイリストを聴いていて……\nもし良かったら共有しましょうか？　おすすめですよ",
      "startTime": 196.4999941507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "どれどれ……おぉ……す、凄いな……\n百曲以上入ってるんじゃないか……？",
      "startTime": 204.999999237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "このプレイリストは二年前の曲を集めたものですね\n激しくて格好いい曲もあれば、可愛い曲もあって！",
      "startTime": 211.799999237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_12_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "こっちのは私が個人的に好きな曲を集めたもので――\nそうだ、今聴いてみましょうか！　解説もつけますよ！",
      "startTime": 220.2333325703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
